    "description": "<strong>《Bloodhunt》是一款驚心動魄的大逃殺遊戲，背景設在布拉格，故事圍繞著各大吸血鬼氏族之間的一場無情鬥爭。在這款第三人稱動作射擊遊戲中，利用你的超自然能力追捕並智取你的仇敵以及審判士兵。做足準備吸食強者的鮮血增強力量，飛簷走壁來去自如，並稱霸黑夜！   </strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/0adfad8eeff785e7a37a56d47faa878a.poster.avif?t=1680688641\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/0adfad8eeff785e7a37a56d47faa878a.webm?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/0adfad8eeff785e7a37a56d47faa878a.mp4?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>超自然戰爭</strong><br>無論你喜歡鬼鬼祟祟地偷襲，還是直接闖入戰場大開殺戒。選擇效命的氏族以利用獨特的超自然能力確定你的遊戲風格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/680c15ba9a7b7892d906fb95a05fc4cb.poster.avif?t=1680688641\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/680c15ba9a7b7892d906fb95a05fc4cb.webm?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/680c15ba9a7b7892d906fb95a05fc4cb.mp4?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>無情支配</strong><br>漫步在布拉格致命的街頭，然後登上屋頂獵食凡人，以增強力量。解決或吸榨每一個阻擋你的敵人，成為最後的贏家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/daf9b8b924dce5837c71caae922f3676.poster.avif?t=1680688641\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/daf9b8b924dce5837c71caae922f3676.webm?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/daf9b8b924dce5837c71caae922f3676.mp4?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>不聖潔同盟</strong><br>独自狩猎，或者召集你的朋友一起进入本能的快节奏战斗，团队合作和战略必不可少。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/16b09ffd75e9ccf5cba499d37012c92b.poster.avif?t=1680688641\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/16b09ffd75e9ccf5cba499d37012c92b.webm?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/16b09ffd75e9ccf5cba499d37012c92b.mp4?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>時髦的捕食者</strong><br>打造專屬造型展現個人特質，讓敵人不記住你也難。利用時髦的服裝以及永不過時的髮型、穿孔或刺青來自訂你的外表，並透過超殺的造型來展現你的個性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/b8428dc328cb22d4987222ea1b8e2e82.poster.avif?t=1680688641\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/b8428dc328cb22d4987222ea1b8e2e82.webm?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/760160/extras/b8428dc328cb22d4987222ea1b8e2e82.mp4?t=1680688641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>《Vampire The Masquerade》傳統</strong><br>《Bloodhunt》的背景是設定在「黑暗世界」宇宙。這可以說是我們現代世界的一個嚴酷版本，吸血鬼就隱藏在我們周遭。他們在對抗著獵人、其他的吸血鬼、以及他們自己的惡劣本能的同時，還必須努力維持著避世偽裝。",
